name: Vessels 122: Dragon Hunter Shielder Kagan
description: Kagan is the first and only ‘Shielder’ in the ranks of Dragon Hunters. A new position means a lot of responsibility and this is to make sure the others don’t burn to death. They were nice enough to give him a warhammer, but the only time he’s used it is in an act of compassion to a viciously charred comrade.
